{"tid":1542169,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎緊將會係六四翻版","createTime":"2019-09-04T18:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T07:22:21.000Z","uid":263577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c7adcd63ee4c845bf1d86d03c9864ba88b730d","tid":1542169,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:35:45.000Z","msg":"睇返30年前64既歷史，當時(4月底)袁木與學生代表創造左對話平台，之後趙紫揚在5月初發表同情學生既演說令到學生以為政府作出讓步，之後曾經一度令學生運動散水，之後在當時(5月上旬至中旬)蘇聯領袖戈巴卓夫訪華時更一度令中共政府在國際傳媒的見證下假裝同情學生，但會晤結束之後，中共便實施了戒嚴，最後就係血腥鎮壓。<br />\n<br />\n而家林奠宣佈動議撤回條例，就係在國際壓力下試圖令事件降溫及淡化焦點。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果港共政府已經完全痴撚左線既話&hellip;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n等到十一之後，佢地就會借復會<span style=\"color: violet;\">突擊硬推送中條例，同時就係實施緊急法、大規模清算、濫捕民主派領袖及昔日雨傘運動既領袖、濫捕市民、強加罪名、甚至殺害市民以儆效尤。</span><br />\n<br />\n中共係64果陣可以無視所有國際壓力同埋制裁，係因為佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">寧願保住權力都唔要錢同埋國際觀感</span>，反正之後搵個國家領導人扮哂開明就得。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中共從來冇真正妥協過！</span></span><br />\n到今日習帝覺得自己係振興中國之光，覺得中國足以超英趕美，好可能都會選擇鞏固權力而不惜一切代價。<br />\n<br />\n香港人係賭緊中共會忌憚一下國際社會同埋美國既壓力，中共係賭緊美國唔會因為香港繼續制裁中國，甚至最終軍事介入挑起戰爭，美國係賭緊中共在多方面理虧再加上經濟損失既情況下最終會接納停止貿易戰既條件，美國今次其實係出師有名。<br />\n<br />\n如果翻版64真係會發生，大家要做好準備，黎緊既日子會好難捱。<br />\n<br />\n希望我係諗錯野，希望林奠係擺左烏龍先會話 「動議撤回」 (雖然我唔覺得會) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc10c007baecf567cdb3c1d66985bc45fbb3d00","tid":1542169,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:36:21.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"54c8525fdc18ecbb30123fc4ee2b9bd321e29bfa","tid":1542169,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:36:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c8f9ceed296b829f2cfae3c32d95fb90ba3c769b","tid":1542169,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:36:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cbf7043d57e9e52c7236f8de480bf9c1ec902d52","tid":1542169,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:38:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0010a9f08fe767adc2b37d7cd54a913dbd1bff95","tid":1542169,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:40:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0aece473d8b4c5463f31bde6badc236f723c7826","tid":1542169,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:41:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a3c73669647a3efbc67125cbbb4466886eea39d","tid":1542169,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:42:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"97f2380ec94df9451c1155e8113e44db28528d35","tid":1542169,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:44:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"758cbd537b330d3261e6c4904ad55012be2fdcf2","tid":1542169,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:19:14.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"97dd57bdd5062b558606879c4d3d636eee1f1dcd","tid":1542169,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:29:02.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9f08ec1cb9d2db686294d8fe69e3d48fc9a4a668","tid":1542169,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:30:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"826832af8c9fac1c33e0c7b9664ed742f9f071dc","tid":1542169,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:01:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62b4a780a3e7f8f798158c050d327b17b2395474","tid":1542169,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:35:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb677845a5307c5b37f57ac78a39bf47bc7325d2","tid":1542169,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:38:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d47e91bf6db45479cddebb8ba82ec0c02c35c935","tid":1542169,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:22:21.000Z","msg":"推"}]}